				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \boldsymbol{\varepsilon} $$\end{document}ε is the estimated error. Five samples on the Agilent platform with largest number of CNPs were determined as outliers and were excluded. Similarly, 61 and 48 normal samples were excluded from Affymetrix and Illumina arrays, respectively. After the removal of outliers, 240, 512 and 466 samples were included for CNP identification on the Agilent, Illumina, and Affymetrix arrays, respectively.

